            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped sweet potato </strong>to the dish with the <strong>onion wedges </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans </strong>and <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife and discard the skins</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1632474592875-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1632474592875-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1632474592875-x700.jpg",
