          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1632474592875-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1632474592875-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> dried oregano</strong> and <strong>crushed garlic</strong> to the dish and stir it all up</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1632474616302-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1632474616302-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1632474616302-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1632474616302-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1632474616302-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> drained black beans</strong> and <strong>drained</strong> <strong>sweetcorn</strong> to the dish with your <strong>tomato paste</strong>,<strong> chipotle</strong> <strong>paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and 650ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[975ml]</span> [1.3L] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>soy sauce </strong>and<strong> </strong>bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cover with the lid and put the dish in the oven for 25 min – this is your<strong> one-pot Mexican-style sweet potato & corn broth</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1632474632916-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1632474632916-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1632474632916-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1632474632916-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1632474632916-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>lime[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Crumble your <strong>Greek cheese</strong> into rough bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1632474661413-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1632474661413-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1632474661413-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1632474661413-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1632474661413-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, add a squeeze of <strong>lime juice </strong>to the <strong>one-pot Mexican-style sweet potato & corn broth</strong> and give it a good mix up</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges, approx. 1 per person</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>crumbled</strong> <strong>Greek</strong> <strong>cheese</strong> over the top and garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
      "order": 8,
